{
  "formatter": {
    "kind": "super-auth",
    "authnType": "&authnType",
    "useAuthz": "&useAuthz",
    "failureAuthAllow": "&failureAuthAllow",
    "bufferSetting": "&bufferSetting",
    "cacheSwitch": "&cacheSwitch",
    "authz_result_cache": "&authz_result_cache"
  },
  "layouts": [
    {
      "key": "authnType",
      "alias": "认证类型",
      "type": "select",
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "网关签名认证",
          "value": "aksk_authn_type"
        },
        {
          "text": "JWT认证",
          "value": "jwt_authn_type"
        },
        {
          "text": "OAuth2认证",
          "value": "oauth2_authn_type"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "useAuthz",
      "alias": "鉴权",
      "help": "开关关闭后，则只会对客户端请求进行认证，所有合法的外部认证都可以访问；开关打开后，会在认证成功后判断对应的外部认证是否被成功授权",
      "type": "switch",
      "default": false
    },
    {
      "key": "failureAuthAllow",
      "alias": "匿名访问",
      "help": "仅对无需鉴权的情况可配置，开启允许匿名访问后，即使认证失败也会将请求继续转发到后端服务，只是转发后相关的认证请求头为空",
      "type": "switch",
      "default": false,
      "visible": {
        "this.useAuthz": false
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "bufferSetting",
      "alias": "请求体配置",
      "type": "layouts",
      "visible": {
        "this.authnType": "aksk_authn_type"
      },
      "layouts": [
        {
          "key": "maxRequestBytes",
          "alias": "最大字节数",
          "help": "请求体参与签名计算，当请求体字节数超过该值，而且允许部分消息开关打开，会截取部分请求体进行签名计算",
          "type": "input",
          "default": "4096",
          "rules": [
            "Number",
            "MinNumber(1)",
            "MaxNumber(1073741824)",
            "Required"
          ]
        },
        {
          "key": "allowPartialMessage",
          "alias": "允许部分消息",
          "type": "switch",
          "help": "该开关打开时，若请求体字节数超过最大请求体，会截取最大请求体长度的消息进行签名计算；否则会拒绝客户端请求",
          "default": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "cacheSwitch",
      "alias": "认证缓存",
      "type": "switch"
    },
    {
      "key": "authz_result_cache",
      "alias": "缓存配置",
      "type": "layouts",
      "help": "配置认证缓存相关信息，包括缓存key以及缓存TTL",
      "visible": {
        "true": [
          "this",
          "cacheSwitch"
        ]
      },
      "layouts": [
        {
          "key": "result_cache_key",
          "alias": "缓存key配置",
          "help": "配置缓存key，默认情况，JWT认证和Oauth2认证采用header:authority,签名认证采用header：x-nsf-accesskey作为缓存key",
          "type": "layouts",
          "layouts":[
            {
              "key": "ignore_case",
              "alias": "忽略大小写",
              "type": "switch",
              "help": "Key忽略大小写",
              "default": true
            },
            {
              "key": "headers_keys",
              "alias": "请求头名称",
              "help": "自定义请求头参与key计算",
              "type": "multi_input",
              "rules": [
                "MaxLength(200)"
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "key": "result_cache_ttl",
          "alias": "TTL(秒)",
          "help": "指定缓存时间",
          "type": "input",
          "rules": [
            "Required",
            "Number",
            "MinNumber(0)",
            "MaxNumber(86400)"
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}